Spa Description: At Fairmont Nile City, spa treatments bring an unrivaled sense of emotional and physical well-being to your stay on the banks of the mighty Nile River. An oasis of soothing Saharan tones, Fairmont Spa evokes Egypt’s natural beauty while inviting you to benefit from the time-honored beauty traditions of its ancient cultures. Expect separate relaxation and changing areas for men and women, luxury treatment rooms (including a dedicated couples’ suite and private hammam), extensive hydrotherapy facilities and a professional hair and nail salon.

Allow us to take you on a journey of guided self- discovery and well-being at Fairmont Spa, your connection to self, others and nature in the heart of Cairo.
